    "Their main objective was to overcome limitations created by small experimental datasets.",
    "To address this, they first developed a comprehensive, multi-cell line, muti-fabrication method dataset through an extensive literature review that connected material properties to CM function.",
    "Subsequently, they identified the most accurate algorithm to predict cell behavior on CTE scaffolds.",
    "Briefly, scaffold materials in this dataset included synthetic and natural materials like polycaprolactone and Fibroblasts-derived ECM.",
    "Fabrication methods in the dataset were comprised of electrospinning, hydrogel encapsulation, and 3D printing among others."
